Package: snomed-diagram-api
Version: 1.1.0
Section: web
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: nodejs (>= 18.0.0), supervisor, chromium-browser
Maintainer: SNOMED International <info@snomed.org>
Description: SNOMED CT Concept Diagram API
 This API provides a way to generate a concept diagram for a given SNOMED CT concept.
 The diagram is generated as an SVG image and returned as a PNG file.
 .
 The service runs on port 3000 and provides endpoints for:
  - POST /diagram - Generate diagram from concept JSON
  - GET /test - Generate example diagram
 .
 This is intended for internal backend use only.
